WEBVTT

00:00:00.279 --> 00:00:03.102
I study the future

00:00:03.102 --> 00:00:07.387
of crime and terrorism,

00:00:07.387 --> 00:00:09.747
and frankly, I'm afraid.

00:00:09.747 --> 00:00:11.709
I'm afraid by what I see.

00:00:11.709 --> 00:00:13.854
I sincerely want to believe

00:00:13.854 --> 00:00:16.646
that technology can bring us

00:00:16.646 --> 00:00:19.703
the techno-utopia that we've been promised,

00:00:19.703 --> 00:00:21.439
but, you see,

00:00:21.439 --> 00:00:24.552
I've spent a career in law enforcement,

00:00:24.552 --> 00:00:27.325
and that's informed my perspective on things.

00:00:27.325 --> 00:00:28.958
I've been a street police officer,

00:00:28.958 --> 00:00:31.029
an undercover investigator,